# Pascal Hügli — Less Noise More Signal
## Three-Part Evergreen Series Blueprint

**Concept.** A reference asset on the LHM framework. Three episodes, one arc: **how we see → how we connect → how we act.** This is the canonical audio reference for the Diagnostic Dozen — what listeners hear *before* they read the Substack series.

**Format.** Episode length isn't capped here — we have the runway to let each episode breathe. Consecutive weeks. Recorded back-to-back if Pascal's calendar allows.

**Pascal's role.** Smart student, not peer. He interrupts with the dumb question; each interruption becomes a teaching moment. Framework readings sent ahead so he isn't catching up in the booth.

