## Defending Against Late-Stage Drift

Pascal tends to change things at the last minute. Countermeasure:

- Send blueprint as: *"Here's the working blueprint. Send edits in writing."*
- **Written-only feedback.** Verbal gets reinterpreted in the booth.
- Lock the structure now so the recording day is execution, not negotiation.
